WEBVTT

00:17.984 --> 00:20.686
Dads <i>is recorded in front of</i>
<i>a live studio audience.</i>

00:23.456 --> 00:25.624
It's 9:00am. Why are you guys
eating spaghetti?

00:25.626 --> 00:28.527
Uh, we're trying to get
inspiration for our mafia game.

00:30.130 --> 00:31.997
Well, how's it going?

00:31.999 --> 00:33.699
(Italian accent):
Not-a so good.

00:35.635 --> 00:37.136
You know, the problem
is you guys are

00:37.138 --> 00:38.804
a couple of rich kids
from the suburbs.

00:38.806 --> 00:40.639
You probably never committed
a crime in your life.

00:40.641 --> 00:41.974
WARNER:
Uh, that's not true.

00:41.976 --> 00:44.309
From to 2000 to 2005,

00:44.311 --> 00:48.180
I stole every piece of music
ever created.

00:48.182 --> 00:51.150
And I once slandered Ke$ha
on an Internet message board

00:51.152 --> 00:52.985
by implying she was
involved in sex acts using

00:52.987 --> 00:55.054
her "A, dollar sign,
dollar sign."

00:57.323 --> 00:59.892
As edgy and dangerous
as you guys are,

00:59.894 --> 01:01.527
I think we should hire
a consultant who knows

01:01.529 --> 01:02.828
what he's talking about.

01:02.830 --> 01:04.196
What do you mean?
Like-like somebody

01:04.198 --> 01:06.065
who's actually
in the mafia?

01:06.900 --> 01:09.001
That's a really
good idea.

01:09.003 --> 01:10.169
No, it's not.

01:10.171 --> 01:11.737
Yeah, it is.

01:11.739 --> 01:13.505
Don't you remember
all the fun we had

01:13.507 --> 01:16.175
with the Nazis we got
for    <i>Kill Hit?</i>

01:16.177 --> 01:18.010
Hey, you know,
maybe we should develop

01:18.012 --> 01:22.014
our driving game
with Lindsay Lohan.

01:22.016 --> 01:24.083
