more of a drinking game.

01:30.023 --> 01:31.223
You know,
you guys, I think

01:31.225 --> 01:34.059
I might be able to help
you find a consultant.

01:34.061 --> 01:37.096
I happen to have had a friend
that was in the mafia.

01:37.098 --> 01:41.700
His name is Johnny Johnny
DeSalvo DeSalvo.

01:41.702 --> 01:44.236
Dad, how do you know
somebody in the mafia?

01:44.238 --> 01:47.072
We tried to set up
a series of Alzheimer clinics

01:47.074 --> 01:50.109
for elderly Italians
called Fuhgeddaboudit.

01:53.213 --> 01:55.714
Wha... what happened?

01:55.716 --> 01:58.016
To what?

02:01.221 --> 02:03.055
Fuhgeddaboudit.

02:03.057 --> 02:04.223
Okay, I will.

02:04.225 --> 02:05.824
Jeez, you brought it up.

