we can't understand?

02:47.268 --> 02:49.768
Oh, I-I watched an episode
of   <i>Soprano</i>last night,

02:49.770 --> 02:52.004
so don't worry,
I got the lingo down.

02:52.006 --> 02:55.607
Oh, the gagoots on
that doorman, huh?

02:55.609 --> 02:58.010
I wanted to give him a
cuestamarole upside his scaputo.

02:58.012 --> 02:59.945
Yeah.

02:59.947 --> 03:02.347
He said he's gonna
have pizza for dinner.

03:04.817 --> 03:06.785
Johnny, this is
my son, Warner.

03:06.787 --> 03:08.120
Oh, nice to meet you.

03:08.122 --> 03:10.522
Whoa. Spaghetti's
been in the pot too long.

03:12.192 --> 03:14.826
Uh, hey, thank you so much
for consulting on our game.

03:14.828 --> 03:16.495
I'm Eli, Warner's
business partner.

03:16.497 --> 03:18.630
What are you,
in kindergarten?

03:18.632 --> 03:21.200
Well, he's
all yours.

03:21.202 --> 03:23.468
All right...

03:23.470 --> 03:27.005
now who do I got to whack around
here to get a tiny coffee?

03:27.007 --> 03:29.975
I'll get that for you.
How do you like it?

03:29.977 --> 03:32.211
Up against the hanging meats
in the back of the deli,

03:32.213 --> 03:34.112
but my coffee I'll take black.

03:35.548 --> 03:38.550
(clears throat)
Wow.

03:38.552 --> 03:41.720
Thank you. Thank you so much
for-for coming down to help us.

03:41.722 --> 03:44.156
M-My dad might have told you
that we're working on a game,

03:44.158 --> 03:45.824
uh, about the, uh...

03:45.826 --> 03:48.160
(whispers):
about the mafia.

03:48.162 --> 03:50.195
Mafia?

03:50.197 --> 03:53.465
You think because I'm Italian-
American, I'm in the Mafia?

03:54.667 --> 03:57.703
Wha... Well,
a-aren't you?

03:57.705 --> 04:00.172
Yeah.

04:00.174 --> 04:03.742
But the point is:
don't make assumptions.

04:04.911 --> 04:06.912
So, San Francisco, huh?

04:06.914 --> 04:09.681
So, what are you, like,
a bunch of fruit loops?

04:09.683 --> 04:11.383
No.

04:11.385 --> 04:14.253
Hey, guys.
Not all of us.

04:19.025 --> 04:21.193
You know, I think we should
get to work on the game

04:21.195 --> 04:23.862
so that Mr. DeSalvo can
get back to the family...

04:23.864 --> 04:24.863
his family.

04:24.865 --> 04:27.733
The-the, uh, normal,
uh, wife and kid...

04:27.735 --> 04:30.369
The, uh, non...

04:30.371 --> 04:33.105
(whispers):
I'm so sorry.

04:33.107 --> 04:36.375
Take a deep breath there,
lady pants.

04:36.377 --> 04:38.710
Now, just
so you know,

04:38.712 --> 04:41.546
I only got one rule:
I do <i>not</i> answer any questions.

04:41.548 --> 04:42.948
Any questions?

04:48.054 --> 04:49.621
Okay, good.

04:49.623 --> 04:52.557
Now, first thing, do not
make all these mob guys

04:52.559 --> 04:54.960
into stereotypical jerks.

04:54.962 --> 04:57.996
(snapping fingers)
Hey, eggroll, start typing.

05:00.600 --> 05:02.601
Then the player finds
out that this magarole's

05:02.603 --> 05:04.069
been skimming
off the top.

05:04.071 --> 05:06.138
So Tony "I Did Your Sister"
Martelli

05:06.140 --> 05:08.206
makes him go for a ride.

05:10.076 --> 05:11.943
