05:15.581 --> 05:18.717
What part of "go for a ride"
do you not understand?

05:22.922 --> 05:24.956
Yes, badafootz.

05:24.958 --> 05:28.960
What if you actually
want to go for a ride?

05:28.962 --> 05:32.831
What am I, a dog
with my head out the window?

05:33.966 --> 05:35.934
Wow, your information
is so well-defined,

05:35.936 --> 05:38.503
it almost makes you think
this stuff really happened.

05:39.672 --> 05:42.941
Are you wearing a wire?

05:42.943 --> 05:45.344
No, I don't wear wires
and I don't carry pennies,

05:45.346 --> 05:49.014
'cause Mexicans will
strip you for the copper.

05:51.951 --> 05:54.019
Mr. DeSalvo, thank you
so much for your help.

05:54.021 --> 05:56.021
I mean, the game
really feels authentic now.

05:56.023 --> 05:58.357
Oh, sure thing, chopsticks.

05:58.359 --> 06:00.158
Oh...

06:00.160 --> 06:03.962
one more very
important detail.

06:03.964 --> 06:05.964
The consigliere
in the game

06:05.966 --> 06:08.033
needs to be
a talking meatball.

06:09.502 --> 06:11.803
A talking meatball?

06:11.805 --> 06:14.206
Yeah. A meatball that knows
all the family secrets,

06:14.208 --> 06:17.476
like who whacked who
what where with what, when.

06:17.478 --> 06:19.010
Plus...

06:19.012 --> 06:21.346
it's funny as hell.

06:21.348 --> 06:23.014
That is
a rib tickler, yeah.

06:23.016 --> 06:24.983
It's... it's amazing,
yeah.

06:24.985 --> 06:27.686
So, now, the, uh,
certain matter of my payment.

06:27.688 --> 06:29.821
Oh, yeah.
Uh, here you go.

06:29.823 --> 06:33.058
I, uh, added an 18%
"Please Don't Kill Us" tip.

06:34.694 --> 06:35.827
Whoa.

06:35.829 --> 06:37.162
What is that, a check?

06:37.164 --> 06:38.997
Y-Yeah.
Uh...

06:38.999 --> 06:40.899
Why? Is that...
is that a problem?

06:40.901 --> 06:42.401
Yes, that's a problem.

06:42.403 --> 06:44.469
I don't have a bank account.

06:46.172 --> 06:48.673
I keep all my money offshore.

06:48.675 --> 06:50.742
In a lobster buoy.

06:51.844 --> 06:53.512
Uh... I don't think
we have that kind of

06:53.514 --> 06:55.680
cash in the...
in the office.
But we can
go to the...

06:55.682 --> 06:57.349
All right.

06:57.351 --> 06:59.251
All right, I'll
tell you what.

06:59.253 --> 07:01.353
Since your old man
is a friend of ours,

07:01.355 --> 07:02.854
we'll call it even.

07:02.856 --> 07:05.690
But at some time in the future,

07:05.692 --> 07:09.461
I may come to you
and ask for a favor.

07:10.863 --> 07:12.431
Sure.
Yeah, sure.

07:12.433 --> 07:16.034
<i>A capilozi vigamo.</i>

07:16.036 --> 07:18.203
