Yeah.

07:31.552 --> 07:34.019
Well, that time has come.

07:39.892 --> 07:41.393
I'm in for ten.

07:41.395 --> 07:42.394
I call.

07:42.396 --> 07:44.095
Call.
Fold.

07:44.097 --> 07:45.397
So this was
the favor?

07:45.399 --> 07:47.232
Yeah. They just wanted
a place to play poker.

07:47.234 --> 07:48.233
