08:45.958 --> 08:47.959
I just hope they wrap
it up before somebody

08:47.961 --> 08:49.961
says something that
could offend them.

08:49.963 --> 08:51.963
So I bought my ma one of them
medical alert bracelets,

08:51.965 --> 08:53.965
