08:59.706 --> 09:02.507
Ha ha ha, he's just
kidding, obviously.

09:02.509 --> 09:04.576
Look at that face.

09:06.379 --> 09:08.813
Oh, yeah,
I get it now.

09:08.815 --> 09:10.982
So, Shecky, why don't
you sit down at the table,

09:10.984 --> 09:11.983
