money to play in a poker game.

09:23.564 --> 09:25.630
Ah.

09:27.333 --> 09:30.402
How about you,
troll on the end of a pencil?

09:33.172 --> 09:35.073
Uh...

09:35.075 --> 09:38.076
Yeah. Yeah, okay,
I'll play a few games.

09:38.078 --> 09:39.411
What?

09:39.413 --> 09:41.046
Yeah, dude.

09:41.048 --> 09:43.615
It's an honor to sit in
a mob poker game.

09:46.085 --> 09:47.719
He's right.

09:47.721 --> 09:49.888
You know, we had several of
those Make-A-Wish kids sit in.

09:49.890 --> 09:52.390
You know, the smiles on their
faces make them almost forget

09:52.392 --> 09:55.026
