10:41.108 --> 10:43.708
No!
Whoa!

10:45.411 --> 10:47.312
(slurring):
Okay!

10:49.915 --> 10:51.082
Salut!

10:51.084 --> 10:52.817
(laughs)

10:52.819 --> 10:54.085
All right.

10:54.087 --> 10:56.755
I see your 20--
