a pretty good hand.

11:00.260 --> 11:02.093
Oh, yeah.

11:02.095 --> 11:03.428
(laughing)

11:03.430 --> 11:05.497
All in.

11:13.005 --> 11:14.506
All in?
(stammers)

11:14.508 --> 11:16.107
I don't...
I don't have as-as much...

11:16.109 --> 11:18.677
many, um, uh... chips as you.

11:20.813 --> 11:22.313
I'll tell you what.
What?

11:22.315 --> 11:25.316
You win, you get
all the money on the table.

11:25.318 --> 11:27.952
I win, I get...

11:27.954 --> 11:29.621
your company.

11:29.623 --> 11:32.123
Aw, you want
