11:43.036 --> 11:45.136
No, I'd have to talk to Eli
about that.

11:45.138 --> 11:46.471
Oh, you hear that?

11:46.473 --> 11:48.640
Chip can't make a move
without checking with Dale.

11:48.642 --> 11:50.709
(men laugh)

11:52.712 --> 11:54.512
I can, too.

11:54.514 --> 11:56.014
All in.

11:56.016 --> 11:59.150
Well, good luck, son.

11:59.152 --> 12:00.885
There's only two hands
that can beat you.

12:00.887 --> 12:02.153
Four aces.

12:02.155 --> 12:04.222
And that's one of 'em.

12:05.858 --> 12:08.493
(panting)

12:08.495 --> 12:10.495
Oh, thank God.

12:10.497 --> 12:12.030
What's the matter,
honey?

12:12.032 --> 12:14.833
Oh, I had the most
insane dream.

12:14.835 --> 12:18.503
Were you an elegant
lady in this one, too?

12:18.505 --> 12:20.839
(knocking)

12:20.841 --> 12:23.007
(screams)

12:23.009 --> 12:24.342
It's a home invasion!

12:24.344 --> 12:26.077
The lady next door
has diamonds

12:26.079 --> 12:29.914
and her alarm password
is "password."

12:29.916 --> 12:32.550
Hey, chipmunk,
you're late for work.

12:32.552 --> 12:35.887
