away to the Mafia.

12:38.225 --> 12:40.024
You what?

12:40.026 --> 12:41.359
Come on, Warner.

12:41.361 --> 12:42.694
You got to get to
work before

12:42.696 --> 12:44.829
all the good tracksuits
are taken.

12:50.102 --> 12:52.103
Where do you get off
gambling away

12:52.105 --> 12:54.372
my half of the company?!

12:54.374 --> 12:57.075
Eli, I-I...
you know, I was drunk.

12:57.077 --> 12:58.109
And-and I was up

12:58.111 --> 13:01.613
eight dollars
before I-I lost the company.

13:02.915 --> 13:04.916
