what rye bread is!

13:32.411 --> 13:37.148
Warner, you got to get all
of this out of here now.

13:40.452 --> 13:43.855
How 'bout a dance, big boy?

13:45.658 --> 13:47.926
Warner, you have got
to get everyone except her

13:47.928 --> 13:49.194
out of here right now.

13:49.929 --> 13:52.130
Hey. What-what's your name?

13:52.132 --> 13:54.199
White Wine.
Yeah, it is.

13:55.935 --> 13:57.836
Hey,

13:57.838 --> 14:01.439
where do you guys keep
your cocaine scale?

14:01.441 --> 14:05.944
Johnny, Johnny,
we-we got to talk.

14:05.946 --> 14:06.978
Sure thing.

14:06.980 --> 14:08.813
I got an open-door policy.

14:08.815 --> 14:10.515
Unless it's a complaint.

14:10.517 --> 14:12.817
Then I got an open
window policy.

14:12.819 --> 14:14.953
Right, fellas?

14:14.955 --> 14:17.288
Oh, they're all out back.
Hey, guys, give me an "Oh!"

14:17.290 --> 14:19.390
MEN:
Oh!

14:20.359 --> 14:21.960
Johnny, I...

14:21.962 --> 14:24.128
